# SkillSync

Sync AI coding skills (Claude Code, Cursor, Codex) across platforms.

**Stack**: Go 1.25.4, urfave/cli v3
**Architecture**: CLI entry in `cmd/skillsync`, core packages in `internal/` (see [docs/architecture.md](mdc:docs/architecture.md))

## Commands
- Build: `just build` | Test: `just test` | Audit: `just audit`
- Run: `./bin/skillsync --help`

## Issue Tracking
- Flow: `bd ready` → `bd show <id>` → `bd update <id> --status in_progress` → `bd close <id>`
- Session completion: `bd sync --flush-only` (local export)
